INFO 2025-12-30 17:40:35,262 views 7 123432443131584 POST data: <QueryDict: {'csrfmiddlewaretoken': ['gtStR2BvCAI4SQYQTVM0JEYhhShGODvy2atxf9rU9sVDCwHX1fvQAfCLxqwmemXV'], 'this_week_work': ['<p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">◆ 대고객 서비스 플랫폼 오픈 지원(~12/22)</span></p><div style="color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp; - 시범운영/그랜드 오픈 일정 및 체크리스트 협의,작성</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp; - 미진사항 점검 및 수행</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2;"><br></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">◆ SAP 권한관리체계 수립(~12월)</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp; - Advanced User Type 분석 및 정리(~11월, 지연)</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp; - 권한관리 현황 보고(본부장님)서 초안 작성</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: bolder;">◆ S/4HANA 전환 검토</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp; - 검토내용 1차 보고(지연)</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: bolder;">◆ 조직개편에 따른 시스템 반영(~12/5)</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp; - 12/5자 조직개편 지원 및 검수</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: bolder;">◆ 내부통제 하반기 운영평가(~12월)</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.2;">&nbsp; - 사전 준비사항 및 일정 협의</p>'], 'files': ['', ''], 'next_week_plan': ['<p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">◆ 대고객 서비스 플랫폼 오픈 지원(~12/22)</span></p><div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;">&nbsp; - 시범운영 오픈 준비 및 점검</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;">&nbsp; - 미진사항 점검 및 수행</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><br></p></div><p style="margin-bottom: 0px;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">◆ SAP 권한관리체계 수립(~12월)</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;">&nbsp; - Advanced User Type 분석 및 정리(~11월, 지연)</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;">&nbsp; - 권한관리 현황 보고(본부장님)</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;">&nbsp; - 미사용 T-code 정리(~12월3W)</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: bolder;">◆ S/4HANA 전환 검토</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;">&nbsp; - 검토내용 1차 보고(지연)</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;">&nbsp; - 타사 현황 검토</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: bolder;">◆ 조직개편에 따른 시스템 반영 후속처리</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;">&nbsp; - 조직개편 작업 후속 모니터링 및 처리</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: bolder;">◆ 내부통제 하반기 운영평가(~12월)</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;">&nbsp; - 모집단 추출 및 제출</p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 1.2; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, sans-serif;"><br></p>'], 'display_order': ['1']}>
